**Output:**

    --- before
    [MyType{name=John&#39;, id=2, author=&#39;author1&#39;, publisher=&#39;publisher1&#39;}
    , MyType{name=Marry&#39;, id=298, author=&#39;author2&#39;, publisher=&#39;publisher2&#39;}
